    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of a Native American tribe in Virginia, originally part of the Powhatan paramountcy in the 17th century. Achieved state recognition in 1985, and is known today as the "Nansemond Indian Nation."</Note_Text>
